Bidvest Says Its Earnings to Benefit From Sale of Stake in Mumbai Airport

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-04T05:08:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/bidvest-says-its-earnings-to-benefit-from-sale-of-stake-in-mumbai-airport.html
  Bidvest Group Ltd. (BVT)  said it expects a
positive impact on headline earnings of between 300 million rand
and 400 million rand from the sale of a stake in Mumbai
International Airport.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
